      "content": "\"let the fight go...\" honestly that sounds so peaceful. it's like i'm just tired of being a person. i feel so stuck, like i'm just waiting for something to happen that will finally make the pain stop. do you think it's ever okay to just want to be with them again? like, to not be alone anymore?",
